<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>ṣwt ạlwrq</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 ṣwt ạlwrq fwq ạlsẖjr kạ̉nh bybsẖr lnạ
 wậdy ạlhwạ wyạ ạlmṭr frḥạn wnfsh yqwl lnạ
 msẖ ṭfl mwlwd wạlslạm dạ jạy ʿly̱ ạlạ̉rḍ ạlslạm
 yfrḥ ạlbsẖryẗ lmạ ymd ạ̹ydh bạlslạm
 wậdy snẗ fạtt kmạn zy ạlly ʿdt qblhạ
 wmhmạ kạn fyhạ ạlly kạn jạyẗ ạbtsạmẗ bʿdhạ
 qṣẗ mylạdnạ mn jdyd wqwlnạ yạ zmạn wʿyd
 ʿn ṭfl ạ̹dạhạ ạlḥyạẗ wkẖly̱ kl ạlkwn sʿyd</lyrics>
